            <description><![CDATA[【🤳🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E9%9D%92%E5%85%89%E7%9C%BC%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E9%9D%92%E5%85%89%E7%9C%BC%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长时间玩手机可能诱发青光眼#</span></a>】急性闭角型青光眼是由于眼球当中的前房角在某种诱因下突然间关闭，而引起眼压短时间内迅速升高的一种眼部疾病。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%85%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%93%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E9%97%AD%E8%A7%92%E5%9E%8B%E9%9D%92%E5%85%89%E7%9C%BC%E5%8F%91%E4%BD%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%85%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%93%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A5%E6%80%A7%E9%97%AD%E8%A7%92%E5%9E%8B%E9%9D%92%E5%85%89%E7%9C%BC%E5%8F%91%E4%BD%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#六大因素易致急性闭角型青光眼发作#</span></a>：①情绪不稳定；②身体疲劳；③眼睛疲劳，长时间、近距离用眼，长时间看手机；④光线的原因，长时间待在较暗的环境中；⑤体位原因，长时间低头；⑥短时间内大量饮水等。 👀<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6jXSwmA" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
